title: The Same Direction
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2VRquFi

by lantia4ever

After seeking a cure for his broken hands in Kathmandu, Stephen Strange suddenly finds himself cast into a world of magic, other dimensions, evil sorcerers and planet-hungry demons. After discovering he’s not the only one who arrived a broken man into Kamar-Taj, power-learning a few magic tricks and meddling with the natural order, he has to soon decide what to do with his newly gained abilities - and his future.

OR

The events of the Doctor Strange movie set in the lovely headcanon verse where Tony Stark visited Kamar-Taj in Iron Man 2 to look for the cure for the palladium poisoning - which he didn’t find. What he did though was become a Master of the Mystic Arts. Vishanti help us all…

summary: — Людям свойственно быть чьими-то. Люди априори принадлежат кому-то, будь то Бог, мама или работодатель. Т-Тони, я люблю тебя. И...
body:
https://my.w.tt/nKRaiqGSYU

— Людям свойственно быть чьими-то. Люди априори принадлежат кому-то, будь то Бог, мама или работодатель. Т-Тони, я люблю тебя. И мне всегда хотелось быть с тем, кто давал бы мне заботу и… нечто похожее на оберегание. Словно я не простой человек из Куинса, а кто-то больше, важнее обычного ребенка.

— Ты стал моей душой. – На выдохе сказал Энтони, припадая к порозовевшим губам юнца. Последний, то ли жалобно, то ли от внезапности заскулил и вплел свои пальцы в волосы старшего, позже сильно сжимая их от пошлого желания.

/


— People tend to be someone’s. People a priori belong to someone, be it God, mother or employer. T-Tony, I love you. And I always wanted to be with someone who would give me care and… something like protection. It’s like I’m not just a person from Queens, but someone more important than a normal child.

— You’ve become my soul. – On the exhale Anthony said, dropping to the pink lips of the boy. Last, whether plaintively, whether from surprise whimpered and wove her fingers into the hair of the older.

body:
Rhodey + Tony

  • You know what I also want? A TV series for Tony and Rhodey in MIT
  • Tony and Rhodey’s first meeting. I always thought it didn’t go well but they actually did warm up to each other

summary: This is for the lovely @drstrangefangirl8900 who asked me some headcanons with this prompt:  So how about after a fight...
body:
This is for the lovely @drstrangefangirl8900 who asked me some headcanons with this prompt: 

So how about after a fight something happens to the nanotech armor mother unit has to be charged and Tony’s hooked it up wires but then he doesn’t want to. the guys force him into it because Ironman needs to be ready all the time. So he has this full blown panick attack infront of all the avengers because it reminds him of afghanistan. He’s hysteric and tears roll down, shivering. That’s when Stephen has had enough….He throws everyone out of the room and carries him to the couch. Takes off the armor from his chest…assures him the wires aren’t attached to his chest but Tony’s shivering in his arms, hiding himself in his chest, clutching into him as if he’ll disappear suddenly and he’ll be alone Stephen carries him to his room, comfort, cuddling… And the avengers say sorry… They’re very guilty. Stephen is like: you should beTony forgives them… But doesn’t move from Stephen’s embrace. He knows he’s safe there.

 This is kind of a headcanon by itself, but I love it so much, so I’ll go with some random fill-up and the likes, hoping you’ll like them <3

1. Tony knows he has to change it, but he doesn’t like to show his chest to people he doesn’t trust because it’s his greatest weakness, and he’s too self-conscious of his scars;

2. Stephen suggests calling Christine of whom Tony trusts to do it (the nanoparticles housing seems to be under Tony skin so I suppose it’s medically implanted in his chest) so that the others can go, but someone insists that they need it now for X reason;

3. So yes, Tony has a panic attack because everyone is screaming and yelling and trying to tell him what to do. Stephen doesn’t want to upset Tony more, so he helps his boyfriend to calm down and then orders everyone to move somewhere else;

4. Once they are alone, Stephen wants to help Tony also because the broken housing is hurting him even if Tony is too panicked to notice. But he can’t because he doesn’t trust his hands enough, and Tony is shaking so bad, so he decides to let him lay on the couch still holding him;

5. When Tony calms down, Stephen calls Christine who helps him with the housing and the Avengers realize what they really asked Tony, and how much this could hurt him;

6. Tony asks Stephen not to leave him during the night and despite his chest being bandaged, he manages to cling on Stephen who’s only happy of that and does everything to be the comfiest boyfriend-pillow as possible.

summary:
‘ au, где питер паркер рассказывает тони старку о его детстве, невольно затрагивая его же мечту настоящего дня. ‘ 
— В детстве...
body:
‘ au, где питер паркер рассказывает тони старку о его детстве, невольно затрагивая его же мечту настоящего дня. ‘


— В детстве меня звали «белой шкуркой», представляешь?


— С чего пошло такое прозвище, солнышко? – Энтони гладит его по плечу и спускается горячими губами к выступающим косточкам ключиц.


— Я носил в те годы белый тулупчик, вот и окрестили меня белой мышью. Жаль, что я из него вырос.


С того дня и появилась у юноши новая белая шубка, ведь Тони поистине нравилось теперь его так называть.


/


‘ au, where Peter Parker tells Tony stark about his childhood, unwittingly affecting his own dream of the present day. ‘


— As a child, I was called “white skin”, can you imagine?


— What’s with the nickname, sweetheart? –Anthony strokes his shoulder and goes down hot lips to the protruding bones of the clavicles.


— I wore during those years, white sheepskin, and that dubbed me the white mouse. I’m sorry I grew out of it.


From that day appeared the young man with a new white coat, because Tony truly liked now to call it that.
